directions: ["Remove flowerets from broccoli, cut into bite-size pieces. Break cauliflower into flowerets.", "Combine broccoli and cauliflower with mushrooms, pepper and celery.", "Toss lightly. Combine remaining ingredients; mix well and pour over vegetables. Chill and serve."]
NER: ["vinegar", "sugar", "stalks celery", "stalks broccoli", "mushrooms", "onion", "poppy seed", "cauliflower", "dry mustard", "vegetable oil", "green pepper", "salt"]

title: Pickled Cukes
ingredients: ["7 lb. cukes, sliced", "1 oz. alum", "3 c. lime", "1 1/2 c. salt", "2 qt. vinegar", "6 lb. sugar", "1/2 box pickling spices"]
directions: ["Soak cukes in lime water overnight (cover).", "Drain and wash 3 times in cold water.", "Soak 2 hours in salt water.", "Drain and wash 3 times in cold water.", "Dissolve alum in warm water.", "Add enough cold water to cover cukes.", "Add cukes and bring to a boil.", "Drain and wash 3 times in cold water.", "Mix sugar, vinegar and spices. Add cukes and bring to a boil, turn down heat and simmer 30 minutes.", "Pack in hot jars.", "Yield: 12 pints."]
